WEBVTT

00:00:02.372 --> 00:00:04.603
Consider the following statement:

00:00:04.627 --> 00:00:08.494
human beings only use 10 percent
of their brain capacity.

00:00:09.230 --> 00:00:11.529
Well, as a neuroscientist, I can tell you

00:00:11.553 --> 00:00:13.656
that while Morgan Freeman
delivered this line

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:16.656
with the gravitas
that makes him a great actor,

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:18.957
this statement is entirely false.

00:00:18.981 --> 00:00:20.061
(Laughter)

00:00:20.085 --> 00:00:24.770
The truth is, human beings use 100 percent
of their brain capacity.

00:00:25.348 --> 00:00:28.903
The brain is a highly efficient,
energy-demanding organ

00:00:28.927 --> 00:00:31.149
that gets fully utilized